skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the voice of laguna
des: Voice Of Laguna radio station gives voice to every corner of the community, and every corner of the world. It is what radio was meant to be, a complete and trusted source of entertainment, information, and most of all, relevance. Musically, it will be an eclectic mix from my Personal Stash of over 300,000 songs, personally curated by me, Mornings With Ed…including NEW artists every day. Important topics, serious conversations with power brokers, policymakers, artists, musicians, and people making a difference. Voice of Laguna believes listeners should have choices…Well, now you do…The Voice Of Laguna.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
